s<\/li>\n<li>Viral videos<\/li>\n<li>Famous figures<\/li>\n<li>Influencers<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Holidays and occasions<\/h3>\n<p>An essential part of your Facebook content plan should be posts devoted to holidays and special occasions. People love to celebrate, and you can spread the feeling of cheerfulness and joy by congratulating them on holidays, or providing them with thematic content (be it a blog post, insightful stats, cards, or video).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/facebook-engagement-post-ideas-holiday-offerings.jpg\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - holiday product promotion example\" width=\"500\" height=\"701\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57684\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/facebook-engagement-post-ideas-holiday-offerings.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/facebook-engagement-post-ideas-holiday-offerings-480x673.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 500px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Holiday Facebook post ideas:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Don&#8217;t miss our <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/holiday-facebook-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">holiday Facebook post ideas here<\/a>!<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gift guides<\/li>\n<li>Announcements of your promos and deals<\/li>\n<li>Customer appreciation posts<\/li>\n<li>Inspiring stories<\/li>\n<li>The plain and simple<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/11\/29\/holiday-customer-appreciation-letter\"> customer greeting<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Advent calendar<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/interactive-facebook-post-ideas-advent-calendar.jpg\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - depositphotos advent calendar example\" width=\"500\" height=\"701\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/interactive-facebook-post-ideas-advent-calendar.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/interactive-facebook-post-ideas-advent-calendar-480x673.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 500px, 100vw\" \/><\/h3>\n<p>An Advent-themed Facebook campaign like the one above by us at Depositphotos is a great way to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/10\/07\/customer-engagement-strategy\">engage with your customers<\/a>, encourage more sales, and attract new followers.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udea8 <strong>Get copy-and-paste social media posts ready for the whole year<\/strong> in our <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.localiq.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteMonthlySocialMediaCalendarTemplate.html?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Template_MonthlySocialMediaCalendar_Download\">free social media template<\/a>!<\/p>\n<div id=\"company-post-ideas\">\n<h2>Engaging Facebook post ideas about your company<\/h2>\n<p>Last but not least are Facebook post ideas about your company. In the world of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/social-media-marketing\">social media marketing<\/a>, you don&#8217;t want every post to directly<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/11\/02\/promote-your-business\"> promote your business<\/a>, so keep a balance and be sure to add value through these posts as much as possible.<\/p>\n<h3>Product updates<\/h3>\n<p>When announcing product updates, share a video tutorial, clarifying caption, and a link to the blog post or page sharing more details. These posts give you the opportunity to answer all the critical questions about the updates and deliver the information in a simple format. For your audience, a post like this is something they can save and quickly access in case any questions arise.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-product-update-example.png\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - product update post example\" width=\"450\" height=\"609\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57695\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-product-update-example.png 450w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-product-update-example-222x300.png 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>More product update Facebook post ideas:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Run a teaser series before the announcement.<\/li>\n<li>Post a video of your product manager announcing the update.<\/li>\n<li>Share three things your customers can do with the new feature.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Company milestones<\/h3>\n<p>Invite your community to celebrate your milestones with you. Not only will they feel valued, but you can<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2015\/07\/10\/brand-awareness\"> increase brand awareness<\/a> and maybe even get some new brand advocates on your side.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-company-milestones.jpg\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - company updates and milestones example\" width=\"500\" height=\"740\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57681\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-company-milestones.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-company-milestones-480x710.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 500px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Milestone Facebook post ideas:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Anniversaries<\/li>\n<li>Awards<\/li>\n<li>nth employee or nth customer<\/li>\n<li>Reached 100, 1,000, etc. followers<\/li>\n<li>Partnerships<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Event announcements<\/h3>\n<p>Is <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/04\/25\/event-marketing\">event marketing<\/a> in your strategy? Facebook is the right platform to communicate with your audience on the topic. You&#8217;ll want to create a Facebook event to allow people to subscribe and follow all the updates, but you should still continue posting announcements, invites, and reminders on your business page.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-event-promotion.png\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - event announcement post example\" width=\"720\" height=\"413\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57696\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-event-promotion.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-event-promotion-480x275.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Event Facebook post ideas:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create an invitation graphic<\/li>\n<li>Create a countdown series<\/li>\n<li>Share custom visuals in line with the event&#8217;s theme<\/li>\n<li>Share photos from the last event<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Testimonial posts<\/h3>\n<p>Not only do customer success stories build trust and help to convert prospects into customers, but they also help to build a community around your brand.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/duolingo\/videos\/716554595993527\/\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-behind-the-lens-example.png\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - behind the lens example\" width=\"720\" height=\"407\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57697\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-behind-the-lens-example.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-behind-the-lens-example-480x271.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Testimonial Facebook post ideas:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Share screenshots of customer reviews<\/li>\n<li>Post a one-minute case study video<\/li>\n<li>Share a short Q&amp;A with your customer<\/li>\n<li>Publish a full testimonial video<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"cute-facebook-post-ideas\">\n<h2>When in doubt, turn to #cutenessoverload<\/h2>\n<p>All the tips shared above require some preparation and time. But what if you run out of Facebook post ideas, get swamped with urgent tasks, forget to schedule a publication, or all of the above?<\/p>\n<p>We\u2019ve all been there, and there\u2019s a quick solution. At Depositphotos, we jokingly call it &#8220;cuteness overload.&#8221; You need to find the funniest, most endearing, or tear-jerking visual you can, come up with a relatable caption, and share it! Audiences love this type of content because it boosts their mood and distracts them from everyday tasks.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-cuteness-overload.png\" alt=\"engaging facebook post ideas - cuteness overload post example\" width=\"720\" height=\"453\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-57698\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-cuteness-overload.png 720w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/engaging-facebook-post-ideas-cuteness-overload-480x302.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Use these Facebook post ideas to increase engagement<\/h2>\n<p>These Facebook post ideas have helped us here at Depositphotos to grow our brand community, spread awareness about our products, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2016\/02\/03\/increase-sales-online\">increase sales<\/a>. To bring results, many of them required brand marketing team resources to develop an effective strategy and commission creative content for Facebook. Although creating truly engaging posts for Facebook might seem like a time-consuming task, your effort will pay you off in the long term.<\/p>\n<h3>About the author<\/h3>\n\n\t\t<div class='author-shortcodes'>\n\t\t\t<div class='author-inner'>\n\t\t\t\t<div class='author-image'>\n\t\t\t<img src='https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/maria-sibirtseva-depositphotos-93813_60x60.png' alt='' \/>\n\t\t\t<div class='author-overlay'><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div> \n\t\t<div class='author-info'>\n\t\t\tMaria Sibirtseva is the Content Team Lead at Depositphotos where she works on creative projects, curates content production, and manages the copywriting department.\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>From polls to pop culture, promotions to puppies, there is something in here for everyone.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":164,"featured_media":58583,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[7],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-57649","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-social-media"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>62 Creative &amp; Engaging Facebook Post Ideas (+Examples!)<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Use these ideas and examples of Facebook engagement pos